<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1946-02-09T16:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1946-02-09T16:00:00-05:00" n="170" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d170">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">835.00/2–846: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Chargé in Argentina</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Cabot</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <gloss target="#t_Niact1"><hi rend="smallcaps">niact</hi></gloss></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1946-02-09T16:00:00-05:00">February 9, 1946—4
                                p.m.</date></dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>227. For Cabot only. We deeply appreciate and have carefully weighed the
                            considerations set forth in <gloss target="#t_urtel1">urtel</gloss> 430,
                            Feb. 8. However, on net balance it has been decided to give statement to
                            press Mon. about 6 p.m. Washington time with 24 hour release date.
                            Summary being cabled in <gloss target="#t_cirtel1">cirtel</gloss><note n="50" xml:id="d170fn50">Not printed.</note> today.</p>
                        <p>Dept feels this is right course action and the one least vulnerable to
                            criticism from points of view of principle and long-range policy and
                            objectives.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Byrnes</hi></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>